(1, 'Hisense 32-Inch Class H4 Series LED Roku Smart TV with Alexa Compatibility (32H4F, 2020 Model)', 'Combining rich 720p picture quality, intuitively smart Roku TV platform, built-in Wi-Fi, and innovative technologies, Hisense H4F series smart TVs are great for all your needs&mdash;streaming, cable, satellite, gaming, and free over-the-air TV.\r\nEnjoy all the key moments in fast-paced sports, movies, and games with motion rate 120-image processing, minimizing picture lag to create a crystal clear image without motion blur.\r\nRoku TV&#039;s simplified home screen and streamlined remote provide easy to access your cable box or HDTV antenna, one-touch access to favorite channels and streaming services, and access to over 5,000 streaming channels and 500,000 movies and TV episodes.\r\nControl the TV with your iOS or android device via the easy-to-use Roku TV remote app, or use your voice to power your TV on and off, change channels, search for shows, and more through an Alexa-enabled device or google assistant (both sold separately).\r\nThe vesa measurements for this TV are 200 x 200mm, for wall mounting purposes. Wall mount sold separately.\r\nMeasuring 28.9 by 17 by 2.8 inches (28.9 by 18.7 by 6.7 inches with included stand, LxWxH), the 32H4F is backed by a one-year manufacturer&#039;s warranty, and includes a Roku remote (batteries included), power cable, and quick start guide.\r\nPower source type: corded electric', '119.99', NULL, 'http://localhost/complete-mvc-framework/public/images/5f9e2233d9833526525a9d5d455dca3df025e919679e0901099d1b6803c92ed545c6680b7e511b06fb2bb104cc1ec3269dd995a833b1ce3785cc5fd1646c4d1b.jpg', '', 'hisense-32-inch-class-h4-series-led-roku-smart-tv-with-alexa-compatibility-32h4f-2020-model', 50, 38, 39, 'portrait', '2020-09-14 11:06:09', '2020-09-14 11:06:09'),
